An included shim kit allows up to 8 different cast and drop configurations; and a new stock and fore end design and rounded trigger give the SBE3 a smoother feel that allow you to shoulder the gun quickly and swing fluidly on passing targets. At the heart of the Super Black Eagle 3 is Benelli's ultra-reliable Inertia Driven™ operating system that cycles 2-3/4", 3", and 3-1/2" shotgun shells interchangeably without adjustments. A Crio® treated barrel and Crio choke tubes produce tight, uniform shot patterns that down birds at maximum shotgun range. The matte finished Super Black Eagle 3 Semi-Auto Shotgun features a rugged, weather-resistant composite stock, and the entire gun is finished in non-reflective black, making it an ideal all-round shotgun for hunters who use a wide range of shotgun ammunition for multiple species
